texts.text: >At a beach somewhere in Tokyo...

*Stretch*
The weather's so nice, it's the perfect time to go surfing...
I need to make the most of today and catch as many waves as I can.
But where should I start... Huh?
>The waves begin to recede at an unnaturally fast pace...

What's going on...?
There's definitely something wrong with these waves.

H-Hey! Everybody, run!
There's a huge wave coming this way!
>The beachgoers start to panic and run...
Why's this happening all of a sudden...?
Wait, that's...!

*Snicker*
How many will I catch this time?!
A demon?! Floating on top of the water...?!
>Meanwhile, at a riverside campground somewhere in Tokyo.

*Scream*
Kazu! Kazu!!

*Cough*
*Hack*
Hey, there's a kid drowning over there!
Hold on! I'll be right there!
N-No, stop...! Geez, he seriously just jumped in...!
Didn't that guy say he came out here to train or something?
That can wait. Right now, we need to find something that can float!
H-Help... Me...!
>The boy struggles to stay afloat...!

Don't worry!
Here, take my hand!

*Cough*
Help...! Help me...!

Huh...?
Are you stuck on something?
>Something is wrapped around the boy's leg below the surface...
Is this...?
Damn...
>The eerie shadow dives down and vanishes...
(It had to be...!!)

*Shiver*
T-This horse monster dragged me down and...
It's okay. You were just caught in some plants.
Our minds tend to wander towards dark places when distressed.
Are you sure...?
I'm certain. Anyway, let's get you back to dry land.
(I'll need to tell Megakin about what I just saw.)
>One week later...
Aight, y'all, here's what we got after a few days of investigatin'. Ready...?
We're gettin' heaps of reports about water-related incidents.
And every time we've gone to take a look, a demon's there wreckin' up the place.
Which explains why so many folks are gettin' hurt.
And even when we deal with it, yo, another one just pops up in its place.
Regular folks can't see these things, so they still don't know what's goin' on,
but it's causin' them to panic and get all hysterical.
Yo, we gotta figure out what's causin' all this.
It looks like these demons tend to show up in certain places too.
Like rivers, swamps, beaches, oceans... Naturally occurin' sources of water.
At least, that's where these things have been hittin'.
But it might be that we just ain't heard about any incidents at pools and stuff yet.
Yo, we're gonna need to cover all our bases with this one.
So here's today's mission, y'all! Good luck!
Please, you two, don't forget that we're not here on vacation...
Okay, okay! I get it!
We're just here to see if any demons have appeared at this pool, right?
Despite how I look, I am keeping my eyes open!
For stuff like... Hey, look at that!
Hurry! Faster!
You're not getting away that easily!
But it's running off somewhere, so should we just leave it alone?
I suppose so. It doesn't seem to be causing any trouble...
Let's leave it.
Let's chase it.
Copy that. Let's just leave it be.
Because the pool's waiting for us!
Aww, do we have to?!
I mean, we're here to watch over the pool, right?
Ririn, didn't I just say that we're not here to have fun?
We need to see if these demons are attacking man-made facilities...
Help! Someone, help!
That Hecate's still here...?
How? It ran way off in that direction a second ago.
Then that means...
*Roar*
>More Hecates come charging towards you!
What the...?
Leave them.
After them!
Wait, Newbie, how can you say that?!
We can't really ignore them anymore at this point!
Yeah, okay...
Ugh! Today was supposed to be about having fun at the pool!
The three of them seem to be headed in the same direction. We mustn't lose sight of them...

I said hurry!
Faster, all of you!
Right, or it'll be too late!
>Even more Hecates appear and run off in the same direction...
I don't think we're gonna lose them now...
So you're saying that all those Hecates ran this way?
And were all gone by the time you got here?
It has been quite a hot day...
I'm fine! We're all fine! Why won't you believe us?!
Also, isn't there an entrance to an Aura Gate here?
It's just a hunch, but...
You decided to call me over because of it.
Still, having demons all funnel into an Aura Gate is very odd...
Wait, do you believe us now?! That means we're right! Right?
I can't say for sure yet...
Something feels... Off... But I can't quite put my finger on what...
Anyway, let's go in and have a look...
But don't let your guard down. We have no idea what's waiting for us inside.
Now, close your eyes and focus...
>Inside the Aura Gate...

Okay, we're in...
But something does seem different...
Yeah, like it really doesn't want us here or something...
Also, is it just me or is it really cold in here?
The color's different.
It's different from normal.
The color? That's an understatement...
You're not wrong, but I can't say specifically why, you know?
It must be because this isn't just any ordinary Aura Gate.
Different from normal? Compared to the usual Aura Gates you've been exploring?
So this isn't just any ordinary Aura Gate?
Good eye, [sys user_name]. Nicely done.
Wait, it's really that different?!
Yes, it is. This all looks very new to me.
I still can't say how or why, but this is very different from what we usually see.
Also, because it's so close to the Aura Gates that the Liberators watch over,
we weren't able to immediately detect it.
And we still don't know if this has anything to do with what's been happening lately...
But ignoring this would also be bad, yes?
Exactly.
I'll let everyone back at the Hideout know.
And we'll start exploring in earnest soon after, so I'll be counting on all of you.
